rows.label: tlk43400441_03_msg0001
rows.name: Hello... How are you all doing?

rows.label: tlk43400441_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I've been using Folta lately to make
some dumplings to give to the kids,
just like Musubi used to do for me.

rows.label: tlk43400441_03_msg0003
rows.name:
They've turned out pretty
good, so the kids pester
me every day for them.

rows.label: tlk43400441_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I'll end up looking like a
dumpling at this rate if I
don't make something else.
